{"type":"message","id":"164edd3d","parentId":"a44cee1a","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:01:03.067Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the issue is clear. AGENTS.md has priority 3 saying ALL album operations should use `dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash`. But only `save` needs vision. The other operations (list, view, search, delete) are pure text/SQL operations.\n\nThe user says \"Override还是加上\" - meaning:\n1. Either override/change the AGENTS.md model routing to not force VL on all album ops\n2. Or add model specification to album_function.md so Son knows\n\nI think the right approach is option 2: add model specification to the album function definition file. That way:\n- `save` action uses VL (needs vision to analyze images)\n- Other actions (list, view, search, delete) don't need VL override\n- AGENTS.md priority 1 says \"功能定义文件已写明 model → 按定义走\" so this is the cleanest\n\nLet me update album_function.md for Son to add model specification, then update the relevant Son spawn example in AGENTS.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_IglwWnK2ZBLTnLkLb03L9451","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/album_function.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## 1. 功能描述\n接收用户发送的图片并附上注释文字，解析注释后一起存入个人相册库，支持按注释内容搜索和按标签浏览。","newText":"## 1. 功能描述\n接收用户发送的图片并附上注释文字，解析注释后一起存入个人相册库，支持按注释内容搜索和按标签浏览。\n\n## 1a. 模型配置\n| 动作 (action) | 模型 | 理由 |\n|---------------|------|------|\n| save | `dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash` | 需视觉模型分析图片内容 |\n| list | 不指定（Son 默认） | 纯文本 SQL 查询 |\n| view | 不指定（Son 默认） | 纯文本 SQL 查询 |\n| search | 不指定（Son 默认） | 纯文本 SQL 查询 |\n| delete | 不指定（Son 默认） | 纯文本 SQL 查询 |"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/album_function.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"## 1. 功能描述\\n接收用户发送的图片并附上注释文字，解析注释后一起存入个人相册库，支持按注释内容搜索和按标签浏览。\", \"newText\": \"## 1. 功能描述\\n接收用户发送的图片并附上注释文字，解析注释后一起存入个人相册库，支持按注释内容搜索和按标签浏览。\\n\\n## 1a. 模型配置\\n| 动作 (action) | 模型 | 理由 |\\n|---------------