{"type":"message","id":"e3f6e98a","parentId":"9fd45eb3","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:01:52.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the first drawing (出租车) was done. The Son subagent completed it successfully, but it didn't use the MEDIA prefix in the response. The second session (163a1bd8) had a MEDIA prefix. Let me check if these images were properly delivered.\n\nThe issue now is: the user is asking \"所以刚才那个图画了吗\" - so was the image drawn? Let me check whether the images were delivered to the user.\n\nThe subagent sessions have deliveryContext with announce mode, so their results would have been auto-announced. But I'm not sure if the MEDIA attachment would have been sent properly in the first one since it just said \"图片路径: draw/draw_00001.png\" instead of using MEDIA prefix.\n\nLet me check the files - both exist:\n- `draw_00001.png` - 1.5MB (出租车)\n- `draw_DRAW-20260605-00002.png` - 1.4MB (排球扣球)\n\nBoth files exist. Let me just show them to the user. I should attach them as media.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"画了，两张。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Jll2P2KCwPory8KzDFKl3959","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/agents/son/sessions/163a1bd8-7de0-4172-ad2c-cfe9630055be.jsonl","limit":5},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/son/sessions/163a1bd8-7de0-4172-ad2c-cfe9630055be.jsonl\", \"limit\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":8124,"output":325,"cacheRead":54528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":227,"totalTokens":62977,"cost":{"input":0.00113736,"output":0.000091,"cacheRead":0.001526784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002755144}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780603308678,"responseId":"bc2519bb-53ae-480e-9dbc-1d251fcf87af"}}
