{"type":"message","id":"6889d4ca","parentId":"8c092919","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:01:57.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the second session was for \"排球场上扣球的激情瞬间\". Both images exist on disk. Let me just show them to the user. The images are at:\n1. `~/.openclaw/workspace-son/draw/draw_00001.png` - 出租车夜景\n2. `~/.openclaw/workspace-son/draw/draw_DRAW-20260605-00002.png` - 排球扣球\n\nThe user asked \"刚才那个图画了吗\" referring to \"刚才那个图\" - they're probably referring to the most recent one. Let me check what was drawn most recently. The first was the taxi (03:54), the second was the volleyball (03:55). Both!\n\nLet me send the images.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"画了，两张都在这儿。\n\nMEDIA:/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/draw/draw_00001.png\n\nMEDIA:/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/draw/draw_DRAW-20260605-00002.png"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":466,"output":217,"cacheRead":62976,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":160,"totalTokens":63659,"cost":{"input":0.00006524,"output":0.00006076,"cacheRead":0.001763328,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001889328}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780603314152,"responseId":"43f73b8d-167f-4c3b-b2e1-f449ab780ec2"}}
