{"type":"message","id":"8bf04de5","parentId":"1be76037","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:10:29.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，所有改完了。总结一下。\n\n改了四个文件：\n\n**album_function.md**\n- 4.1 save: `MEDIA:album/images/...` → `FILE:/root/.openclaw/.../album/images/...`\n- 4.4 view: 同上\n- 第6节说明更新\n\n**draw_function.md**\n- 4.1 step 6: 新增 `FILE:/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/draw/draw_{id}.png`\n- 第6节示例更新\n\n**compose_function.md**\n- 4.1 step 8-9: `<qqmedia>` → `FILE_AUDIO:` / `FILE_BIN:` 路径行\n- 第6.1节示例更新\n\n**AGENTS.md**\n- 3.3 Step 3: 完整文件转发规则（扫 FILE: 标记 → 转 MEDIA/qqmedia → 删标记行 → 发）\n\nSon 不能再直接发出图片/音频了，先回我这中转。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完事了。改的是这几个：\n\n| 文件 | 改了什么 |\n|------|---------|\n| `album_function.md` | save/view 的 `MEDIA:` → `FILE:` 绝对路径 |\n| `draw_function.md` | 新增 `FILE:` 路径标记，去掉 `{附图片}` |\n| `compose_function.md` | 去掉 `<qqmedia>` 嵌入，改用 `FILE_AUDIO:` / `FILE_BIN:` |\n| `AGENTS.md` 3.3 Step 3 | 加了文件转发规则：扫标记 → 转 MEDIA/qqmedia → 删标记 → 发 |\n\nSon 那边就算 auto-announce 推送了也只是纯文本带 `FILE:` 行，不会有残废附件。我收到后再生成 MEDIA 发出去，路径也不会有问题。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":450,"output":397,"cacheRead":98176,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":220,"totalTokens":99023,"cost":{"input":0.000063,"output":0.00011116000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002748928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002923088}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780603824125,"responseId":"85194a44-ba19-4dfb-9462-3efd765081b1"}}
