{"type":"message","id":"e32a2c74","parentId":"82ebec07","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:14:45.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问我刚才那张图片是啥。我看到的只有QQ Bot自动生成的Description文本，没有实际看到图片。让我描述一下我看到的内容：\n\n\"刚刚又一段 Description 过来了。描述文本说是一个浅色猫咪戴着红色麦当劳帽，灰色耳机，表情又拽又困。但这只是文字描述啊——我没看到图。\"\n\n他问\"我刚才那个图片是啥\" - 他看到我回了那段描述，但想确认我到底看到了什么。 \n\n让我直接告诉他我看到的就是那段Description文本，没有原图。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"就是那段 `Description:` 呀——一只浅色猫，戴红色麦当劳帽+灰色耳机，表情又拽又困，背景深色砖墙，插画风格。\n\n但是我看到的只有这堆文字，没看到图本身。所以如果你问\"看起来是什么样\"，我只能把那段英文描述念给你听😅\n\n不过说真的——你连着发两张图过来是想测QQ Bot的图片描述能力？还是想让我干点什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":678,"output":204,"cacheRead":99584,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":109,"totalTokens":100466,"cost":{"input":0.00009492,"output":0.00005712,"cacheRead":0.002788352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002940392}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780604080668,"responseId":"1db3a415-6151-45db-8886-0e290199e292"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bda0562e","parentId":"e32a2c74","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:15:17.592Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"[Image]\nUser text:\n[qqbot 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 Fri 2026-06-05 04:15 GMT+8]\nDescription:\nA female superhero with spiky black hair and intense blue eyes charges forward, fists clenched. She wears a white and purple costume with a stylized “S” emblem on her chest. Radiating red lines behind her suggest speed or power. A speech bubble reads: “我想和你做的事可比打架激烈多了.” (I want to do things with you that are far more intense than fighting.)","timestamp":1780604115888,"MediaPath":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/5C90121A6FDCBCE624A434239FB09115_1780604113409_4a025d.jpg","MediaPaths":["/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/5C90121A6FDCBCE624A434239FB09115_1780604113409_4a025d.jpg"],"MediaType":"image/jpeg","MediaTypes":["image/jpeg"]}}
