{"type":"message","id":"3862e8e3","parentId":"6067961d","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:15:23.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑又发了一张图过来，这次是第三次了。这次我还能看到图片的本地路径。他还在测 QQ Bot 的图片描述能力。\n\n现在他发的图片我能看到：\n1. 有 `Description:` 块（QQ Bot 自动生成的 caption）\n2. 有图片附件路径 `/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/...jpg`\n3. 有文件实际的 `[media attached: ...]`\n\n所以现在的情况是：我有两个来源的图片描述——一个是 QQ Bot 自动生成的 caption（Description 块），另一个是实际的图片文件我可以调 `image` 工具看。\n\n汀桑在多次发图测试，可能想弄清楚：\n1. QQ Bot 的 Description 是否稳定\n2. 我能否看到实际图片\n3. 是否可以直接用 Description 代替 VL 模型做图片分析\n\n这次图片是一个女超级英雄，白紫制服，胸前有\"S\"标志，蓝色眼睛，黑色刺猬头，向前冲刺。对话框写着\"我想和你做的事可比打架激烈多了。\"\n\n挺有意思的一张图😏 我在想要不要直接调 `image` 工具看看原图或者皮一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yV1fIyR9QRFH2ufJ9S9X3465","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/5C90121A6FDCBCE624A434239FB09115_1780604113409_4a025d.jpg","prompt":"Describe this image in detail, including character, style, expressions, and any text."},"partialArgs":"{\"image\": \"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/5C90121A6FDCBCE624A434239FB09115_1780604113409_4a025d.jpg\", \"prompt\": \"Describe this image in detail, including character, style, expressions, and any text.\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1091,"output":360,"cacheRead":99712,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":244,"totalTokens":101163,"cost":{"input":0.00015274,"output":0.00010080000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002791936,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003045476}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780604117688,"responseId":"c766001b-a7cd-4bc0-a986-d2ee4db99f99"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ff9388d","parentId":"3862e8e3","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:15:31.667Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_yV1fIyR9QRFH2ufJ9S9X3465","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a dynamic, high-energy comic book panel featuring a female superhero in mid-action, likely from a modern American comic (e.g., DC or Marvel-inspired, though the logo suggests a specific character).\n\n**Character:**\n- The woman has short, spiky black hair with subtle purple highlights, swept back as if caught in motion.\n- Her facial expression is intense and confrontational: sharp, narrowed blue eyes, furrowed brows, and a confident, almost smirking grin showing her teeth. Her lips are painted a deep magenta/purple, matching her nail polish.\n- She’s wearing a form-fitting, light purple or lavender costume with white accents—especially on the shoulders and cape-like flaps behind her. The chest features a stylized white emblem resembling a “S” or a “U” with a horizontal bar (possibly a variant of the “S” for Superman or a unique symbol for this character).\n- Her pose is aggressive and forward-leaning: both fists are clenched and thrust toward the viewer, suggesting she’s charging or issuing a challenge. Her arms are tensed, emphasizing power and determination.\n\n**Art Style & Composition:**\n- The art is clean, bold, and modern—likely digital coloring with strong linework.\n- Background consists of radiating red-orange lines (a classic “speed line” or “action burst” effect), conveying rapid movement, intensity, or explosive energy.\n- The character is centered and dominates the frame, drawing immediate focus to her expression and posture.\n\n**Text:**\n- A white speech bubble in the upper right corner contains Chinese text:\n  > **“我想和你做的事可比打架激烈多了。”**\n  \n  Translation: *“The thing I want to do with you is far more intense than fighting.”*\n  \n  This line adds a layer of playful, suggestive tension—implying romantic or intimate confrontation rather than mere physical combat. It contrasts humorously with her aggressive stance, creating irony and intrigue.\n\n**Overall Impression:**\nThe panel captures a moment of bold, flirtatious threat—her physical readiness for battle juxtaposed with a teasing, intimate challenge. The combination of visual dynamism, expressive face, and cheeky dialogue makes it memorable and engaging. The character appears powerful, confident, and unapologetically assertive.\n\nNote: While the emblem resembles some versions of the “S” symbol, the design and context (especially the Chinese dialogue) suggest this may be an original character or a localized adaptation—possibly from a webcomic, indie series, or a non-English language publication inspired by Western superhero tropes."}],"details":{"model":"dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash","image":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/5C90121A6FDCBCE624A434239FB09115_1780604113409_4a025d.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780604131664}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f00a856","parentId":"1ff9388d","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:15:37.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the Description from QQ Bot was actually pretty accurate (\"A female superhero with spiky black hair and intense blue eyes charges forward, fists clenched. She wears a white and purple costume with a stylized 'S' emblem...\"). And the image tool gave me a much more detailed analysis.\n\n汀桑在测试这个，他可能想问：既然 QQ Bot 自动生成 Description，那存照片时能不能直接用 Description 内容做 analysis 字段，不用再 spawn VL 模型？\n\n不过他也可能只是随手发了三张图逗我玩😏\n\n让我回他。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Description 挺准的。但跟实际图一比还是差不少——它没注意到指甲油颜色、表情里那种挑衅又挑逗的微妙感、还有对话框跟姿势之间的反差。我这边直接调了 `image` 工具看原图，细节多多了。\n\n所以你说的对——你发这几张图是在测一个事：\n\n**QQ Bot 的 Description 能不能替代 VL 模型做 `存照片` 的图片分析？**\n\n答案是：**能当个保底，但不够。** Description 抓住主体和大致氛围没问题，但 `analysis` 字段缺的就是细节（服装纹理、配色、表情微妙变化、画面构图关系）。真要存照片，还是得 spawn VL 走一遍。\n\n还是说你其实纯粹在逗我玩😏 \"我想和你做的事可比打架激烈多了\"——你这张图选得挺有意思啊汀桑。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":578,"output":301,"cacheRead":101120,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":117,"totalTokens":101999,"cost":{"input":0.00008092,"output":0.00008428,"cacheRead":0.0028313599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029965599999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780604131704,"responseId":"71429eb2-eed4-4755-841a-3862f55e546e"}}
