{"type":"message","id":"b6d4ed92","parentId":"827c2e92","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:24:35.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the first Son spawn (session c00b61cb) actually completed successfully! It analyzed the image (a cocktail menu) and saved it to the album. The result includes a FILE: path. It took 3m26s which is long but it worked.\n\nThe second spawn (session 713f807b) failed because the image wasn't in context.\n\nSo Son did manage to analyze it - the image was somehow available to Son. Maybe the QQBOT channel attaches the image to the subagent context automatically? Or maybe the first spawn captured the image in time.\n\nAnyway, the result is here. I need to follow the 3.3 Step 3 rules:\n1. Scan for FILE: lines - found `FILE:/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/ALB-20260605-0001.jpg`\n2. Remove FILE: line from text\n3. Emit MEDIA: for the FILE path\n4. Send text + MEDIA to user\n\nLet me forward the result to 汀桑 with the MEDIA attachment. The image is already saved in Son's album directory.\n\nActually wait - I also need to check what description Son generated for the analysis. The result only shows the basic save info without the analysis description. Let me check - it says \"📸 已存 1 张照片！\" with ID and \"查看全部: /看相册\". No description or tags since annotation was empty.\n\nBut the real analysis (the VL description) might be in the database. Let me just forward what Son returned. The main point is that Son DID successfully analyze the image via VL and save it.\n\nLet me send it to 汀桑 following the forwarding rules.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"第一个 spawn 跑完了，成功分析了图也存了。按 3.3 Step 3 转发给你——\n\nMEDIA:/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/ALB-20260605-0001.jpg\n\n📸 已存 1 张照片！\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nID: ALB-20260605-0001\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n查看全部: /看相册\n\n所以 Son 其实能拿到图——第一个 spawn 成功了，花了三分多钟。第二个我之前无脑又点了一次那个失败的才报没数据。\n\n纯图片走 Son VL 是可行的，但耗时 3min+。你觉得这个延迟能接受？还是说我直接自己调 image tool 更快，规则里写两个方案都行？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":106335,"output":576,"cacheRead":4736,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":377,"totalTokens":111647,"cost":{"input":0.014886900000000002,"output":0.00016128,"cacheRead":0.000132608,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015180788}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780604664856,"responseId":"cf8197e9-ac24-4e32-9af4-e8a0e023bb0b"}}
