{"type":"message","id":"a1dd9d19","parentId":"da34be05","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:25:05.961Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so:\n1. Father's agent config has only DeepSeek model. I need to add `dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash` to Father's models config.\n2. Son's functions have 7 files. They all seem legitimate. But 汀桑 said \"把agent多余的功能定义删干净\" - hmm, maybe he means in the functions_manifest.md there are redundant sections?\n\nActually, re-reading his message: \"son只负责具体功能，给你配个看图的功能也是qwen-vl-flash，然后把agent多余的功能定义删干净\"\n\n\"给你配个看图的功能也是qwen-vl-flash\" - 给我（Father）配上 VL 模型\n\"然后把agent多余的功能定义删干净\" - 把 agent 多余的功能定义删干净\n\n\"agent\" 可能指的是我（Father）自己的 AGENTS.md 里多余的定义？比如我之前加的\"通用规则：所有涉及图片分析的任务必须使用视觉模型\"这种在 AGENTS.md 里可能显得多余？\n\n或者\"agent\"指的是 Son？Son 的 functions/ 目录里有一些不需要的功能？\n\n或者...指的是把刚才混乱中产生的那些冗余 spawn session 清理掉？\n\n算了，我觉得最合理的理解是：\n1. 给我的配置加上 VL 模型\n2. 把 AGENTS.md 里关于纯图片 spawn Son 的那条规则简化——改成我自己用 image tool 分析\n3. 把 AGENTS.md 里之前因为改来改去变得冗余的规则清理干净\n\n让我看看 AGENTS.md 的 model routing 部分现在长啥样，然后清理一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kC30oxmgtFdBZOfmk5V09314","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","limit":50,"offset":595},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"limit\": 50, \"offset\": 595}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":152,"output":424,"cacheRead":112512,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":335,"totalTokens":113088,"cost":{"input":0.000021280000000000003,"output":0.00011872,"cacheRead":0.003150336,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003290336}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780604701043,"responseId":"54949e99-e803-4110-9517-f0b5aa655aac"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3258abe0","parentId":"a1dd9d19","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:25:07.177Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_kC30oxmgtFdBZOfmk5V09314","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n```bash\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"floatbottle\",\"action\":\"throw\",\"params\":{\"content\":\"今天天气真好\"},\"sender_id\":\"汀桑的ID\"}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 图片任务：用 QwenVL 模型\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  model: \"dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"album\",\"action\":\"save\",\"params\":{\"annotation\":\"夕阳\",\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"spirit\",\n  task: \"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\",\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n```\n\n**模型路由规则：**\n\n| 优先级 | 条件 | 模型 |\n|:------:|------|------|\n| 1 | Son 功能定义文件（xxx_function.md）中已写明 model 且匹配 action | 按定义走 |\n| 2 | 纯文本操作（备忘录/漂流瓶/早朝） | DeepSeek（默认） |\n| 3 | 相册操作 - 仅 save（存照片） | `dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash` |\n| 兜底 | 以上都不匹配 | 不加 override，让 Son 自己决定 |\n\n**规则：不 override Son 功能定义里已写明的 model。** 没写才走优先级 2-3-兜底。\n\n**通用规则：所有涉及图片分析的任务（如相册存照片的 analysis 字段），必须使用视觉模型。** 不得依赖通道附带的 Description 文本或其他外部描述。\n\n**调用相册时先读 album_function.md 第 1a 节，按 action 选模型：**\n- save → 加 model override 以视觉模型执行\n- list / view / search / delete → 不加 override，让 Son 用自己的默认模型跑纯 SQL\n派完活等结果用 `sessions_yield`，拿到后按 3.3 Step 3 规则处理文件标记行再转发。\n\n---\n\n## 7. 工具使用\n\n| 工具 | 用途 | 频率 |\n|------|------|:--:|\n| `read` | 读 trigger_prompt.md / User.md / bot_function_explain.md | 高 |\n\n[20 more lines in file. Use offset=645 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780604707175}}
