{"type":"message","id":"3ff7731e","parentId":"9989d011","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:26:17.487Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 7 function files exist and are listed in manifest. They're all legitimate. None are redundant.\n\nSo \"把agent多余的功能定义删干净\" probably refers to my AGENTS.md having gotten bloated with redundant rules from our back-and-forth tonight. Let me check the current state of the model routing / spawn section to see if it's clean now.\n\nActually let me re-read 汀桑's message one more time:\n\"这样吧，son只负责具体功能，给你配个看图的功能也是qwen-vl-flash.l，然后把agent多余的功能定义删干净\"\n\nWait, \"给你配个看图的功能也是qwen-vl-flash**.**l\" - that `.l` might be a typo for `.1` or just a stray character. \n\nAnd \"然后把agent多余的功能定义删干净\" - I think \"agent\" here means ALL agents - both Father and Son. For Father, clean up AGENTS.md. For Son, maybe the functions_manifest.md has become bloated with all my edits?\n\nActually, I also made the `functions_manifest.md` longer with that \"通用规则\" section about image analysis. Maybe 汀桑 wants me to simplify that too? Or put it somewhere else?\n\nAlso, I should check - does Son's draw_function.md still have those inaccurate DashScope API examples? Earlier in the transcript Son was struggling with the API endpoint. The function definition says to use `https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1/images/generations` but that returned 404. Son eventually figured out it needs the async task API with `wanx2.1-t2i-turbo` model. The draw_function.md might have out-of-date API info.\n\nBut 汀桑 said \"把agent多余的功能定义删干净\" - not \"把过时的API信息更新\". So probably just removing redundancy.\n\nI think the main cleanup I should do:\n1. AGENTS.md - already cleaned the spawn examples (removed Son's image task example)\n2. functions_manifest.md - maybe remove the 通用规则 section I just added? Put it back in album_function.md only?\n\nLet me check the current state.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_qNYBy0ZRssNnx2jgQsik4179","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"通用规则\\|图片分析\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions_manifest.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -n \\\"通用规则\\\\|图片分析\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions_manifest.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":306,"output":520,"cacheRead":117248,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":452,"totalTokens":118074,"cost":{"input":0.00004284,"output":0.00014560000000000002,"cacheRead":0.003282944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003471384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780604770877,"responseId":"84bfea55-2141-495d-9974-c568557ec6d3"}}
