{"type":"message","id":"9db7b500","parentId":"ce3de72f","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:26:34.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me check the AGENTS.md routing section to make sure it's clean and not redundant.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞完了。总结改动：\n\n**openclaw.json — Father 配了 VL 模型**\n```json\n\"models\": {\n  \"deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash\": {\"alias\": \"DeepSeek\"},\n  \"dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash\": {\"alias\": \"Qwen3VlFlash\"}\n}\n```\n\n**AGENTS.md — 清理三处**\n- 去掉了\"图片任务用 QwenVL 模型 spawn Son\"那个示例（Son 自己的功能定义文件管它自己的模型，我不用替它写示例）\n- 纯图片路由改成只 spawn Son，不再手动 override model（album_function.md 第 1a 节已写清楚 save 用 VL）\n- 加了一句：纯图片我也可以直接用 `image` 工具自己看，不必绕 Son\n\n**functions_manifest.md — 去除冗余的通用规则节**\n规则写在各功能定义文件（album_function.md 4.1 step 5）和 AGENTS.md 里就够了，manifest 不存业务规则。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":118,"output":245,"cacheRead":119040,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":22,"totalTokens":119403,"cost":{"input":0.00001652,"output":0.0000686,"cacheRead":0.0033331199999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00341824}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780604790362,"responseId":"ef287fa5-393b-484f-accf-82ecc377ea3c"}}
