{"type":"message","id":"ff6a6587","parentId":"e9d7ff7e","timestamp":"2026-06-04T20:27:17.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK done. Now the pure image handling is clear: I use image tool myself, no Son, no accidental save.\n\nLet me also check if the album_function.md's save action has the right annotation flow for when params has empty annotation - it should still save fine since annotation can be empty string.\n\nActually the save flow: step 3 says \"整段文字作为 annotation（注释正文）\" and \"放到 analysis(AI按要求解析内容)\". If annotation is empty string, it still saves. The image gets VL-analyzed and stored. That's fine for /存照片. But for pure image messages, the user didn't ask to save.\n\nLet me reply to 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"修好了。问题出在路由定义直接写了 `album action=\"save\"`，语义就是\"存照片\"，Son 照章办事没毛病。\n\n现在纯图片消息不 spawn Son 了，我用 `image` 工具自己看，不走 album save 那条路。\n\n刚不小心存进去的那张鸡尾酒菜单要删掉吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":59,"output":214,"cacheRead":121600,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":140,"totalTokens":121873,"cost":{"input":0.00000826,"output":0.00005992,"cacheRead":0.0034048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00347298}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780604833368,"responseId":"e9bc951e-410e-4583-b4a1-1735c01bc99b"}}
